{"id":"pau","term":"Pau","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:39\">Gen. 36:39</a>) or Pai (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 1:50\">1 Chr. 1:50</a>), bleating, an Edomitish city ruled over by Hadar.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 36:39","1 Chronicles 1:50"]}